_pRange.descriptionZh: 个人或组织公布的需求，用于寻求某种商品或服务。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A pointer to products or services sought by the organization or person (demand).
_pRange.rdfs:label: seeks

_properties.descriptionZh: 卖家接受的支付方式，现金、信用卡等。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The payment method(s) accepted by seller for this offer.

_properties.descriptionZh: 预定资源需要提前的时间数（例如预定火车票需在发车前至少一小时）
_properties.rdfs:comment: The amount of time that is required between accepting the offer and the actual usage of the resource or service.
_properties.rdfs:label: advanceBookingRequirement

_properties.descriptionZh: 服务或产品所覆盖的区域。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The geographic area where a service or offered item is provided.
_properties.rdfs:label: areaServed

_properties.descriptionZh: 比如有现货，无现货，需要预定 等
_properties.rdfs:comment: The availability of this item—for example In stock, Out of stock, Pre-order, etc.
_properties.rdfs:label: availability

_properties.descriptionZh: 此报价中物品或服务的下架，下市时间
_properties.rdfs:comment: The end of the availability of the product or service included in the offer.
_properties.rdfs:label: availabilityEnds

_properties.descriptionZh: 此报价中物品或服务的上架、上市时间
_properties.rdfs:comment: The beginning of the availability of the product or service included in the offer.
_properties.rdfs:label: availabilityStarts

_properties.descriptionZh: 可以获得此报价的地方（比如说商店位置）
_properties.rdfs:comment: The place(s) from which the offer can be obtained (e.g. store locations).
_properties.rdfs:label: availableAtOrFrom

_properties.descriptionZh: 报价所支持的物流递送方式，例如当日到达，隔日到达，邮局包裹等
_properties.rdfs:comment: The delivery method(s) available for this offer.
_properties.rdfs:label: availableDeliveryMethod

_properties.descriptionZh: 商业职能，如销售，维修，储藏
_properties.rdfs:comment: The business function (e.g. sell, lease, repair, dispose) of the offer or component of a bundle (TypeAndQuantityNode). The default is http://purl.org/goodrelations/v1#Sell.
_properties.rdfs:label: businessFunction

_properties.descriptionZh: 就是指收到订单和货物离开仓库或准备取件（如果是上门取货的话）之间的延迟。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The typical delay between the receipt of the order and the goods either leaving the warehouse or being prepared for pickup, in case the delivery method is on site pickup.
_properties.rdfs:label: deliveryLeadTime

_properties.descriptionZh: 哪些顾客适用于这个报价，例如促销折扣仅适用于60岁以上客户。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The type(s) of customers for which the given offer is valid.
_properties.rdfs:label: eligibleCustomerType

_properties.descriptionZh: 报价的有效时间，例如促销折扣仅限于某一周有效。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The duration for which the given offer is valid.
_properties.rdfs:label: eligibleDuration

_properties.descriptionZh: 报价最多可有购买多少货品，例如每客户最多可以购买一个优惠产品。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The interval and unit of measurement of ordering quantities for which the offer or price specification is valid. This allows e.g. specifying that a certain freight charge is valid only for a certain quantity.
_properties.rdfs:label: eligibleQuantity

_properties.descriptionZh: 报价适用的区域，例如免运费仅限于北京三环内用户。
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The ISO 3166-1 (ISO 3166-1 alpha-2) or ISO 3166-2 code, the place, or the GeoShape for the geo-political region(s) for which the offer or delivery charge specification is valid.

See also ineligibleRegion.
_properties.rdfs:label: eligibleRegion

_properties.descriptionZh: 适用适用的最低消费，例如满100免运费。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The transaction volume, in a monetary unit, for which the offer or price specification is valid, e.g. for indicating a minimal purchasing volume, to express free shipping above a certain order volume, or to limit the acceptance of credit cards to purchases to a certain minimal amount.
_properties.rdfs:label: eligibleTransactionVolume

_properties.descriptionZh: 12位全球贸易品项识别码
_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-12 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. The GTIN-12 is the 12-digit GS1 Identification Key composed of a U.P.C. Company Prefix, Item Reference, and Check Digit used to identify trade items. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin12

_properties.descriptionZh: 13位全球贸易品项识别码
_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-13 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. This is equivalent to 13-digit ISBN codes and EAN UCC-13. Former 12-digit UPC codes can be converted into a GTIN-13 code by simply adding a preceeding zero. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin13

_properties.descriptionZh: 14位全球贸易品项识别码
_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-14 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin14

_properties.descriptionZh: 8位全球贸易品项识别码
_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-8 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. This code is also known as EAN/UCC-8 or 8-digit EAN. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin8

_properties.descriptionZh: 包含的对象
_properties.rdfs:comment: This links to a node or nodes indicating the exact quantity of the products included in the offer.
_properties.rdfs:label: includesObject

_properties.descriptionZh: 不适合区域
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The ISO 3166-1 (ISO 3166-1 alpha-2) or ISO 3166-2 code, the place, or the GeoShape for the geo-political region(s) for which the offer or delivery charge specification is not valid, e.g. a region where the transaction is not allowed.

See also eligibleRegion.
_properties.rdfs:label: ineligibleRegion

_properties.descriptionZh: 当前产品的库存量
_properties.rdfs:comment: The current approximate inventory level for the item or items.
_properties.rdfs:label: inventoryLevel

_properties.descriptionZh: 预定义值
_properties.rdfs:comment: A predefined value from OfferItemCondition or a textual description of the condition of the product or service, or the products or services included in the offer.
_properties.rdfs:label: itemCondition

_properties.descriptionZh: 销售的物品
_properties.rdfs:comment: The item being offered.
_properties.rdfs:label: itemOffered

_properties.descriptionZh: 产品的制造商零件编号（MPN）或提供者对产品的引用
_properties.rdfs:comment: The Manufacturer Part Number (MPN) of the product, or the product to which the offer refers.
_properties.rdfs:label: mpn

_properties.descriptionZh: 一个或多个详细的价格规格，表示单价和交货或付款费用。
_properties.rdfs:comment: One or more detailed price specifications, indicating the unit price and delivery or payment charges.
_properties.rdfs:label: priceSpecification

_properties.descriptionZh: 提供商品出售、物品租赁、贷款等服务的人或组织。
_properties.rdfs:comment: An entity which offers (sells / leases / lends / loans) the services / goods.  A seller may also be a provider.
_properties.rdfs:label: seller

_properties.descriptionZh: 此产品的序列号。序列号是由一系列数字和字母数字组成的标识符。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The serial number or any alphanumeric identifier of a particular product. When attached to an offer, it is a shortcut for the serial number of the product included in the offer.
_properties.rdfs:label: serialNumber

_properties.descriptionZh: 最小库存单元是指包含特定的自然属性与社会属性的商品种类，在零售连锁门店管理中通常称为“单品”。当一种商品而言，当他的品牌、型号、配置、花色、容量、生产日期、保质期、用途、价格、产地等属性与其他商品存在不同时，就是一个不同的最小存货单元。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The Stock Keeping Unit (SKU), i.e. a merchant-specific identifier for a product or service, or the product to which the offer refers.
_properties.rdfs:label: sku

_properties.descriptionZh: 有效开始日期
_properties.rdfs:comment: The date when the item becomes valid.
_properties.rdfs:label: validFrom

_properties.descriptionZh: 有效截止日期
_properties.rdfs:comment: The date after when the item is not valid. For example the end of an offer, salary period, or a period of opening hours.
_properties.rdfs:label: validThrough

_properties.descriptionZh: 报价中包含的担保承诺
_properties.rdfs:comment: The warranty promise(s) included in the offer.
_properties.rdfs:label: warranty

_pTree.descriptionZh: 一个需求实体表示公众，不一定有约束力，不一定唯一，由某一组织或个人宣称，追求某一类型的物品或服务。为了描述使用这种类型的需求，使用与Offer完全一样的属性。
_pTree.rdfs:comment: A demand entity represents the public, not necessarily binding, not necessarily exclusive, announcement by an organization or person to seek a certain type of goods or services. For describing demand using this type, the very same properties used for Offer apply.
_pTree.rdfs:label: Demand

_properties.descriptionZh: 该项的一个附加类型， 通常用于从外部词典中向微数据语法添加更加具体的类型。它表示事物和事物本身所属的类之间的关系。在RDFa语法中, 对多类型最好使用‘typeof’属性这样的本地RDFa语法. Schema.org 工具对额外类型的理解较弱，特别是外部定义的额外类型。
_properties.rdfs:comment: An additional type for the item, typically used for adding more specific types from external vocabularies in microdata syntax. This is a relationship between something and a class that the thing is in. In RDFa syntax, it is better to use the native RDFa syntax - the 'typeof' attribute - for multiple types. Schema.org tools may have only weaker understanding of extra types, in particular those defined externally.
_properties.rdfs:label: additionalType

_properties.descriptionZh: 该项的别名。
_properties.rdfs:comment: An alias for the item.
_properties.rdfs:label: alternateName

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 比如有现货，无现货，需要预定 等
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The availability of this item—for example In stock, Out of stock, Pre-order, etc.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: availability

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 此报价中物品或服务的下架，下市时间
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The end of the availability of the product or service included in the offer.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: availabilityEnds

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 此报价中物品或服务的上架、上市时间
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The beginning of the availability of the product or service included in the offer.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: availabilityStarts

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 可以获得此报价的地方（比如说商店位置）
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The place(s) from which the offer can be obtained (e.g. store locations).
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: availableAtOrFrom

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 报价所支持的物流递送方式，例如当日到达，隔日到达，邮局包裹等
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The delivery method(s) available for this offer.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: availableDeliveryMethod

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 商业职能，如销售，维修，储藏
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The business function (e.g. sell, lease, repair, dispose) of the offer or component of a bundle (TypeAndQuantityNode). The default is http://purl.org/goodrelations/v1#Sell.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: businessFunction

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 就是指收到订单和货物离开仓库或准备取件（如果是上门取货的话）之间的延迟。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The typical delay between the receipt of the order and the goods either leaving the warehouse or being prepared for pickup, in case the delivery method is on site pickup.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: deliveryLeadTime

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 哪些顾客适用于这个报价，例如促销折扣仅适用于60岁以上客户。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The type(s) of customers for which the given offer is valid.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: eligibleCustomerType

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 报价的有效时间，例如促销折扣仅限于某一周有效。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The duration for which the given offer is valid.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: eligibleDuration

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 报价最多可有购买多少货品，例如每客户最多可以购买一个优惠产品。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The interval and unit of measurement of ordering quantities for which the offer or price specification is valid. This allows e.g. specifying that a certain freight charge is valid only for a certain quantity.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: eligibleQuantity

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 报价适用的区域，例如免运费仅限于北京三环内用户。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment:
The ISO 3166-1 (ISO 3166-1 alpha-2) or ISO 3166-2 code, the place, or the GeoShape for the geo-political region(s) for which the offer or delivery charge specification is valid.

See also ineligibleRegion.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: eligibleRegion

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 适用适用的最低消费，例如满100免运费。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The transaction volume, in a monetary unit, for which the offer or price specification is valid, e.g. for indicating a minimal purchasing volume, to express free shipping above a certain order volume, or to limit the acceptance of credit cards to purchases to a certain minimal amount.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: eligibleTransactionVolume

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 12位全球贸易品项识别码
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-12 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. The GTIN-12 is the 12-digit GS1 Identification Key composed of a U.P.C. Company Prefix, Item Reference, and Check Digit used to identify trade items. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: gtin12

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 13位全球贸易品项识别码
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-13 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. This is equivalent to 13-digit ISBN codes and EAN UCC-13. Former 12-digit UPC codes can be converted into a GTIN-13 code by simply adding a preceeding zero. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: gtin13

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 14位全球贸易品项识别码
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-14 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: gtin14

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 8位全球贸易品项识别码
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-8 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. This code is also known as EAN/UCC-8 or 8-digit EAN. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: gtin8

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 包含的对象
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: This links to a node or nodes indicating the exact quantity of the products included in the offer.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: includesObject

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 不适合区域
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment:
The ISO 3166-1 (ISO 3166-1 alpha-2) or ISO 3166-2 code, the place, or the GeoShape for the geo-political region(s) for which the offer or delivery charge specification is not valid, e.g. a region where the transaction is not allowed.

See also eligibleRegion.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: ineligibleRegion

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 当前产品的库存量
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The current approximate inventory level for the item or items.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: inventoryLevel

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 预定义值
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: A predefined value from OfferItemCondition or a textual description of the condition of the product or service, or the products or services included in the offer.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: itemCondition

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 销售的物品
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The item being offered.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: itemOffered

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 产品的制造商零件编号（MPN）或提供者对产品的引用
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The Manufacturer Part Number (MPN) of the product, or the product to which the offer refers.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: mpn

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 一个或多个详细的价格规格，表示单价和交货或付款费用。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: One or more detailed price specifications, indicating the unit price and delivery or payment charges.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: priceSpecification

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 提供商品出售、物品租赁、贷款等服务的人或组织。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: An entity which offers (sells / leases / lends / loans) the services / goods.  A seller may also be a provider.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: seller

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 此产品的序列号。序列号是由一系列数字和字母数字组成的标识符。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The serial number or any alphanumeric identifier of a particular product. When attached to an offer, it is a shortcut for the serial number of the product included in the offer.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: serialNumber

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 最小库存单元是指包含特定的自然属性与社会属性的商品种类，在零售连锁门店管理中通常称为“单品”。当一种商品而言，当他的品牌、型号、配置、花色、容量、生产日期、保质期、用途、价格、产地等属性与其他商品存在不同时，就是一个不同的最小存货单元。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The Stock Keeping Unit (SKU), i.e. a merchant-specific identifier for a product or service, or the product to which the offer refers.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: sku

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 有效开始日期
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The date when the item becomes valid.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: validFrom

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 有效截止日期
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The date after when the item is not valid. For example the end of an offer, salary period, or a period of opening hours.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: validThrough

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 报价中包含的担保承诺
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The warranty promise(s) included in the offer.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: warranty

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 个人或组织公布的需求，用于寻求某种商品或服务。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: A pointer to products or services sought by the organization or person (demand).
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: seeks

rdfs:comment: A demand entity represents the public, not necessarily binding, not necessarily exclusive, announcement by an organization or person to seek a certain type of goods or services. For describing demand using this type, the very same properties used for Offer apply.
rdfs:label: Demand
